# Work package hygiene

## Naming

`[NN][parallel]-[task-slug]-[project].md`

- **Sequential:** `01-flexbox-engine-layout-system.md`
- **Parallel streams (same prereq):** `02A-grid-layout-system.md` + `02B-header-body-layout-system.md`
- Letters = parallel batches after the prerequisite number (**02A/B**, never `01A` when dependency is `01`)

## Structure

- **Single artifact:** optional lone `docs/implementation/01-task-foo.md`
- **Package:** `docs/implementation/<project>/_OVERVIEW.md` + numbered tasks in the same directory (see **`define-project` / `define-tasks`** skills).
- **_OVERVIEW:** no dependency ASCII art — Dependencies field per work package is enough.

## Completion

- Single definition of ✅ done (criteria + Final Steps) — don’t triple it across sections.
- When finishing: update **`_OVERVIEW`** status / % / short note only; skip extra README/rules unless the WP demands it.

## WP fields

Capture **In / Out scope**, **Prerequisites**, **Provides**, **Blocks**; parallel work → note conflicting files upfront.

Routing + commands: **`project-workflow.mdc`** + **`define-*` / `implement-task` skills**.
